name: Town Jjhief
content: Um, um. You are cool! I can trust you.

name: Town Jjhief
content: The Exam monster is very dangerous. You need to hide your identity.

name: Town Jjhief
content: I will give you a new name.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Your new name, squeak, from now on…!

name: Town Jjhief
content: How is it? Do you like it?

name: Town Jjhief
content: Please repel the Exam monster and bring peace to our town.
